author: Von Clownstick

comment:
Saw this movie yesterday. I went into the theatre without expecting much since it's a DC movie, but I came out with my mind blown. Very fun, very entertaining, beautiful world building and superb action sequences.

The action, oh my god, is like Batman's Warehouse fight in BvS, that level of quality in every fight. It isn't just brute force and power, it actually portrays skill between the fighters. Nicole Kidman and Amber Heard actually killed it, powerful female action leads, like you wouldn't believe. Patrick Wilson as Orm, the best fighter there, not a great villain, but the best warrior. Loved the Ending of the movie, not the cliche villain forces the hero to kill him or kills himself kind of thing. It's simply awesome... 

I hope they keep this up! In my opinion, they should wait a few years before planning a sequel, take their time with the plot and build the universe from there...
